FBIS4-45464 "jptdd027__l94042" JPRS-TDD-94-027L JPRS Narcotics 13 June 1994 AFRICA GHANA Narcotics Board Announces 1993 Drug Seizures, Arrests Narcotics Board Announces 1993 Drug Seizures, Arrests AB1406153094 Accra Ghana Broadcasting Corporation Radio Network in English 1800 GMT 13 Jun 94 AB1406153094 Accra Ghana Broadcasting Corporation Radio Network English BFN [Text] The Narcotics Control Board said today that it has announced that the security agencies seized 1.739 million kg of cocaine, heroin, and Indian hemp in 1993 and arrested 147 drug peddlers during the period. According to figures released by the board, the haul is an increase on 1.471 million kg seized in 1992 during which 87 people were arrested. The board said, however, that in view of inadequate facilities, the figures quoted fall below the actual trend. It said 71 Ghanaians were arrested outside the country, mainly in the United States and Thailand.
